    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/1e8b81c67b6be30799f9bb09d3351eb7.poster.avif?t=1765990722\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/1e8b81c67b6be30799f9bb09d3351eb7.webm?t=1765990722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/1e8b81c67b6be30799f9bb09d3351eb7.mp4?t=1765990722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伴着节奏，揍翻敌人！</h2>《Crypt of the NecroDancer》是一款屡获殊荣的硬核 Roguelike 节奏游戏。踩着节奏，探索变幻的地牢，大战狂舞的骷髅、僵尸、巨龙等强敌。伴着 Danny Baranowsky 创作的超抓耳原声舞动，还可自行导入你所珍藏的 MP3！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/951a978b9a49af3c74498a2d6a28519f.poster.avif?t=1765990722\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/951a978b9a49af3c74498a2d6a28519f.webm?t=1765990722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/951a978b9a49af3c74498a2d6a28519f.mp4?t=1765990722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可使用多达 15 名角色攻关地牢，玩法与难点各不相同！</li><li>由 Danny Baranowsky 创作的原声带曾获大奖，包含超过 40 首精彩原创音乐！还可根据玩家自己的 MP3 文件生成谱面！</li><li>一步一个谐音梗，处处都有冷笑话！</li><li>键盘、手柄甚至跳舞毯，全部支持！</li><li>官方《弹丸论破》联动角色皮肤，外加官方模组支持！</li><li><strong>额外惊喜：</strong>全部原声音乐均附带 6 个混音版本。混音由 FamilyJules、A_Rival、Chipzel、OCRemix、Girlfriend Records 与 Virt 倾情奉献！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/247080/extras/4e312b8e9bc2086b9d3961b6718b6e4c.avif?t=1765990722\" width=614 height=204 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >金银财宝，任你探寻</h2>收集钻石即可解锁永久升级、获得更强装备，助你深入死灵舞者的老巢。越是深入，你所遭遇的敌人也将越为凶险狡诈。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高分速通，巅峰决斗</h2>踩着迪斯科舞步深入地牢，并不妨碍勇攀高峰。无论你的目标是最高分数还是最快通关，都有活跃而忠实的玩家社区与你相互切磋；项目既有长远目标，也有每日挑战，每名角色都有属于自己的赛道。",
